NK100(the)014:1: // bdud las rnam rgyal man ngag bzhugs /
NK100(the)014:2: bla ma rin po che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK100(the)014:3: bsam gtan bdud las rnam rgyal ba'i man ngag 'di la gsum ste /
NK100(the)014:4: klad kyi don du bstan pa /
NK100(the)014:10: gzhung gi don la gsum ste /
NK100(the)014:11: gnas lugs ye sangs rgyas pa la gang zag gi
NK100(the)014:12: dbang po dang rtog pa'i bye brag gis dbye ba
NK100(the)014:13: bstan pa dang / gzhung don dngos dang /
NK100(the)014:14: 'jug bsdus te rang sems dag na bdud las grol bar bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:16: bdud du bzhag tu yod med kyi bye brag bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:17: rtogs na ci dang ci byed pa byang chub kyi spyod par bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:18: ma rtogs na ci dang ci byed pa bdud kyi las la spyod par bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:19: gong ma ltar yin pas bdud ngo shes par bya
NK100(the)014:20: zhing bdud dbang du mi 'gro bar bya ba 'og
NK100(the)014:21: tu ston par dam bca' ste /
NK100(the)014:24: rtsa ba bsdom bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:25: yan lag dgrol ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:29: byin gyis rlob lugs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:30: g.yob cing rlong pa bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:33: grogs slob kyi tshul bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:35: rtsa ba sdom dang yan lag bsgrol ba dang /
NK100(the)014:37: yan lag bsgrol ba la gsum ste /
NK100(the)014:38: cher 'jug pa dang mi 'jug pa bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:39: dbang du 'gro ba dang mi 'gro ba bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:40: ye 'jug pa dang mi 'jug pa'i bye brag brtsi ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:42: rtsa ba sdom bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:45: yan lag dgrol ba la gnyis te /
NK100(the)014:46: sdom bcu gcig dgrol bar bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:47: gnyis kyi dbye' ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:49: drug dang mi ldan bco lnga'i rtags bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:50: bcu gnyis kyi rtags bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:52: drug dang mi ldan pa'i bco lnga bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:55: rtsa ba sdom bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:56: yan lag dgrol ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:57: bcu dang gnyis kyi rtags la lnga ste /
NK100(the)014:58: tshogs lam sdom dang sbyor lam dang /
NK100(the)014:59: sa'i bcu gnyis bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:60: tshogs lam bzhi'i yan lag dgrol ba bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:61: rtse mor phyin pa sbyor ba'i rtags bcu gnyis dang /
NK100(the)014:62: drod chen po'i rtags bcu gnyis dang /
NK100(the)014:63: lam so so'i rtags spyir shes par bya ba'o //
NK100(the)014:64: ji ltar byin gyis barloba pa la gsum ste /
NK100(the)014:68: yan lag bsgrol ba la gsum ste /
NK100(the)014:69: 'dod pa'i lha chung ba dang bcas pa'i las bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:70: 'khor 'jig skyong ba bzhi'i la bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:71: bdud kyi rigs kyi yi dwags dang bcas pa'i las gang yin pa bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:72: g.yob cing rlong pa la gnyis te /
NK100(the)014:73: g.yob pa bcu drug bdud kyi rkyen dang zas su bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:74: zhi bar bya ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:76: rtsa ba sdom bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:77: yan lag dgrol ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:79: thun mong ma yin brtan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:82: bco lnga sngar bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:86: tha ma rlung byang chub sems dpa' khros pa bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:87: 'brel ba la sogs pa'i bdud zhi bar bya bar bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:88: rlung byang chub sems dpa' khros pa'i bdud la gsum ste /
NK100(the)014:89: rtsa ba sdom bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:90: yan lag dgrol ba bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:92: yan lag bsgrol ba la gnyis te /
NK100(the)014:93: rten gyi drod tshad bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:96: rtsa ba sdom bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:97: yan lag bsgrol ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:99: blo che bas mnyam pas bzlog pas zhi thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:100: 'bring gis rang sems bcos pas zhi thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:101: tha ma'i zhi thabs drug bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:103: snying rjes gnas pas zhi thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:104: ngo shes bor bas zhi thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:105: sbyin bsreg bstan pas zhi thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:106: bsod nams spel bas zhi thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:107: 'tshams bcad pas zhi thabs bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:108: rdzas kyi brtul zhugs kyis zhi thabs bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:109: grogs slob kyi tshul la gnyis te /
NK100(the)014:110: rtsa ba sdom bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:111: yan lag bsgrol ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:113: skyon bcu tshan bzhi bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:114: drug tu rtogs par bya ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:116: grogs kyi skyon bcu tshan dang po bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:117: grogs kyi skyon bcu tshan gnyis pa dang /
NK100(the)014:118: slob dpon dang slob ma'i skyon bcu tshan gnyis bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:119: drug tu nges par rtogs par bya ba la drug ste /
NK100(the)014:120: rnal 'byor pa dang chos pa la grogs yon tan
NK100(the)014:121: dang ldan pa rten par gces pas grogs brtags par
NK100(the)014:122: bstan pa dang / rnal 'byor bsgrub pa po la
NK100(the)014:123: slob dpon rtag par shin tu ces pas bstan pa
NK100(the)014:124: bstan pa dang / dang / dbang bskur ba'i slob dpon dang /
NK100(the)014:125: slob ma chos 'di lta bu dang ldan dgos pa bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:126: nyan bshad kyi slob dpon dang /
NK100(the)014:127: slob ma batsa'i bstan pa dang /
NK100(the)014:128: man ngag btsal ba dang sbyin pa'i chos batsa'i ba bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:129: sems bskyed pa dang sdom pa dbog pa'i slob dpon dang slob ma batsa'i bstan pa'o //
NK100(the)014:130: bsam gtan bdud las rnam par rgyal ba'i 'byed 'grel /
NK100(the)014:131: gong ma'i yi ge las bla ma'i gsung bzhin bag tsam bcos pa'o //
